  <summary date="2022-01-13T15:28:36Z" status="Introduced in Senate">End Government Shutdowns Act 

This bill provides continuing appropriations to prevent a government shutdown if any appropriations measure for a fiscal year has not been enacted before the fiscal year begins or a joint resolution making continuing appropriations is not in effect.</summary>
